# Content Source

- **Runtime JSON**: `public/assets/data/portfolio.json` — loaded by `data.js` at fetch time.
- **Bundled fallback / transforms**: `public/assets/js/data.js` (`PORTFOLIO_DATA`, `_applySectionSubs`, `_partnersFromExperience`).
- **CV reference**: `docs/cv-modern-template.md` — do not invent employers, dates, or titles.
- **Legacy seeds** (when syncing): `portfolio-v2/codes/database/seeders/data/` in the sibling docker repo.
- **Sections map**: `portfolio.json` → `sections` keys (`about`, `services`, `experience`, …) → `[data-sec-sub]` in HTML.
- **Experience**: Brain Station 23 = four roles in one group; `toggleRole(id)` per role; point list uses `.point-chip` check markers.
- **Brand pills**: `brandOf(item)` → `{ color, mono, icon }`; add entries to `brands` map + SVG in `public/assets/img/brands/`.
- **Per-role tech**: `stacks[]` and `aiTools[]` on each experience role → `.brand-pill` rows under `.role-tags`.
- **Partners**: derived from experience logos + `brandColors` slug map; rendered as `.partner-pill` in hero.
